  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nDealers are currently in heavy buying mode as SPX (6548.76) sits below the GEX flip at 6580 and near the massive negative gamma wall at 6500 (-9.6B), forcing them to buy every dip to hedge their short gamma exposure. The PIN regime with this GEX profile creates a magnet effect toward 6580 where dealers will flip to selling pressure, making 6580 the key resistance level to watch for mean reversion. Expect continued dealer buying support around current levels with accelerating buying if we approach 6500, but any push above 6580 triggers dealer selling into strength.",
